OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FThousands of people have descended on
OL,7,FWimbledon Park hoping to bag a ticket
OL,8,Fto the tennis championships, with some
OL,9,Fplaying ball games and others
OL,10,Fcelebrating birthdays.
OL,12,FMore than 9,000 people had joined the
OL,13,FWimbledon queue, according to an event
OL,14,Fsteward, with many camping overnight
OL,15,Fin tents or arriving in the early
OL,16,Fhours of Monday morning.
OL,18,FThe park was filled with people
OL,19,Frelaxing on picnic blankets, playing
OL,20,Fgames and cracking open cans of beer
OL,21,Fand bottles of prosecco.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
