OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FCivil servant Tom Spencer joined the
OL,7,Fqueue for the tournament on Sunday
OL,8,Fafternoon, with friends gathered to
OL,9,Fcelebrate his birthday wearing
OL,10,Fcolourful party hats.
OL,12,FMr Spencer, from Finsbury Park, north
OL,13,FLondon, said it was his idea to
OL,14,Fcelebrate his 26th birthday ` which
OL,15,Fhas fallen on the first day of the
OL,16,Ftournament ` trying to secure tickets.
OL,18,FHe said: "I looked up when Wimbledon
OL,19,Fwas on and it happened to coincide
OL,20,Fwith my birthday, so I thought,
OL,21,F'right, that's the perfect excuse'.
OL,26,@zD@JOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,F"I was going to go anyway, but this
OL,7,Fwas a good opportunity to get loads of
OL,8,Fpeople there together, and, to some
OL,9,Fextent, it's free camping in London,
OL,10,Fessentially.
OL,12,F"And the facilities are pretty good `
OL,13,Fno showers, though."
OL,15,FMr Spencer said he and his friends had
OL,16,Fpassed the time with "lots of drinks"
OL,17,Fand takeaway pizza ` an order they
OL,18,Fwaited two hours for
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@TO]xD@VOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
