CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FHe said: "I just like going there
OL,7,F(Wimbledon) for the coffee and having
OL,8,Fa beer and watching it
OL,10,F"I think we're slightly short of the
OL,11,Fbig tickets. I saw Emma Raducanu
OL,12,Fdropped out, that would have been
OL,13,Freally good."
OL,15,FThe British number one pulled out of
OL,16,FWimbledon on Sunday evening, after a
OL,17,Fscan showed a leg injury she had been
OL,18,Ftrying to overcome had become a stress
OL,19,Ffracture.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
