OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FStudent Hannah Turcinova travelled to
OL,7,Fthe tournament from the Czech
OL,8,FRepublic, arriving in the queue at 2pm
OL,9,Fon Sunday ` the earliest people are
OL,10,Fasked to arrive.
OL,12,FMs Turcinova, 19, said: "We came at
OL,13,F2pm, and we thought there would be no-
OL,14,Fone. That was the original time on the
OL,15,Fwebsite... and it was written, 'please
OL,16,Fdon't come before this time'.
OL,18,F"So next time, we're definitely going
OL,19,Fto come in the morning."
OL,26,@tD@YOUzD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
