PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FShe said: "It (camping) was a pleasant
OL,7,Fexperience. People are just coming
OL,8,Faround you and want to chat. Very
OL,9,Flovely.
OL,11,F"Nobody's trying to get in front of
OL,12,Fyou, everyone's just at their side."
OL,14,FSam Shepherd, from Penrith, Cumbria,
OL,15,Fsaid her and her friends had spent
OL,16,Fmuch of their time joining queues for
OL,17,Fother things, such as coffee or
OL,18,Fluggage storage.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUtD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
