FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FMs Shepherd, 53, arrived at 3pm on
OL,7,FSunday and camped overnight, enjoying
OL,8,Fa "good atmosphere", but not the early
OL,9,Fwake-up call from stewards.
OL,11,FShe said: "They did wake us up half-an-
OL,12,Fhour early, they woke us up at 5am.
OL,14,F"They come round and go, 'morning,
OL,15,Feverybody up, get your tents packed
OL,16,Faway'."
OL,18,FShe said: "I would recommend a
OL,19,Fblackout tent ` it's quite nice
OL,20,F(keeping it) dark still."
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@SO]sD@KOUvD@AOUxD@GO]zD@KOU|D@
OL,26,AYO]
