FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FMr Mangalidan, from Brentford, west
OL,7,FLondon, said: "It got colder in the
OL,8,Fmiddle of the night. After this little
OL,9,Fheatwave, I didn't expect that."
OL,11,F"I didn't even bring a jumper," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FA woman who did not want to be named
OL,15,Fsaid she was supposed to be at work on
OL,16,FMonday but made a spontaneous decision
OL,17,Fto join the queue overnight instead,
OL,18,Farriving at 3am.
OL,26,@oD@OOUqD@`O]sD@AOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
