FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1782812888
OL,3,CBall games and birthdays: Thousands
OL,4,Cjoin queue for first day of Wimbledon
OL,6,FShe said: "I'm supposed to be at work
OL,7,Ftoday, but my cousin's come in from
OL,8,FVancouver and she's a really big
OL,9,Ftennis fan.
OL,11,F"She's visiting family in London, so I
OL,12,Fthought, 'let's make this happen for
OL,13,Fher'."
OL,15,FShe added: "I only have one sleeping
OL,16,Fbag, and we don't know where it is...
OL,17,Fso we just got mats and some blankets,
OL,18,Fand we slept on the ground. It was
OL,19,Fquite cold actually."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUuD@FO]wD@LOU{D@UO]
